Display Land Registry Transaction available categories

Source: R/avail-uktrans.R
uktrans_avail_items.Rd

uktrans_avail_items() and uktrans_avail_regions() display available items and regions for search respectively.

uktrans_avail_items()

uktrans_avail_regions()

Value

Returns a character vector.

Examples


uktrans_avail_items()
#>  [1] "DFLCount"                      "DLGCount"                     
#>  [3] "FRCount"                       "TPCount"                      
#>  [5] "OSPCount"                      "OSWCount"                     
#>  [7] "OSNPWCount"                    "OC1Count"                     
#>  [9] "SIMCount"                      "OSNPPCount"                   
#> [11] "OC2Count"                      "totalApplicationCountByRegion"
uktrans_avail_regions()
#>  [1] "South East"                     "West Midlands"                 
#>  [3] "South West"                     "North West"                    
#>  [5] "Wales"                          "East Midlands"                 
#>  [7] "Greater London"                 "North"                         
#>  [9] "Isles of Scilly"                "East Anglia"                   
#> [11] "England & Wales (not assigned)" "Yorks & Humber"
